  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>Reach your destination by plane</h2>
<p>Reach your destination by plane and let your walking adventure take flight. View all our 23/24 holiday destinations you can reach by plane.</p>
<p><img src="/media/13088428/travel-requirements.jpg" alt="planehero" data-udi="umb://media/9a2a2327fa7e4579958798d3f8e76cae" /></p>
<p>With departures from airports located throughout the UK, finding a flight that fits your holiday plans is a breeze. Get yourself to your chosen airport and we'll take care of the rest, with return transfers between your airport and your accommodation in resort. With our representatives at most airports or on the phone, we're all about ensuring your journey is smooth from take-off to touchdown.</p>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">View Our Holiday Destinations</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;">See all the countries and their resorts that you can reach by plane for your 2024/25 holiday.</p>
